UID:87392-1776882600-1776890700@bangaloreinternationalcentre.org
SUMMARY:TechnoCats
DESCRIPTION:86 minutes | English with subtitles | 2026 \nOne million applicants. Seven seats. Then what? \nSeven young people from across India fight their way into IIT\, only to find that getting in was the easier part. The filmmaker\, an IIT alumnus himself\, spent seven years with them\, from their first semester to the third year of their careers. \nDecades after graduating\, Gautam Sonti recognised in these students the same pressure he had once felt: a system that measures everything and nurtures very little. TechnoCats is his attempt at a conversation across generations. \nThe screening will be followed by a discussion between Gautam Sonti\, Tara Rao and Aunohita Mojumdar\, before opening to audience questions. \nWatch the trailer here. \nIn collaboration with: \n \n
URL:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/event/technocats/
LOCATION:Bangalore International Centre\, 7\, 4th Main Road\, Domlur II Stage\, Bangalore\, Karnataka\, 560071\, India
CATEGORIES:Education,Film,Society
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Thumbnail_TC.jpg
END:VEVENT
